# Platform Backend Design System

## Component Mapping (MANDATORY)

Files inside `src/components/platform/` MUST use platform-specific UI primitives:

| Base (PROHIBITED)                              | Platform (USE INSTEAD)                                      |
|------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardTitle`, etc.        | `PlatformCard`, `PlatformCardHeader`, `PlatformCardTitle`   |
| `Badge`                                        | `PlatformBadge`                                              |
| `Button`                                       | `PlatformButton`                                             |
| `Input`                                        | `PlatformInput`                                              |
| `Select`, `SelectTrigger`, `SelectContent`     | `Select`, `PlatformSelectTrigger`, `PlatformSelectContent`   |
| `Label`                                        | `PlatformLabel`                                              |
| `Table`, `TableHead`, `TableRow`, `TableCell`  | `PlatformTable`, `PlatformTableHead`, `PlatformTableRow`, `PlatformTableCell` |
| `DialogContent`, `DialogTitle`, `DialogDescription` | `PlatformDialogContent`, `PlatformDialogTitle`, `PlatformDialogDescription` |
| `AlertDialogContent`, `AlertDialogTitle`, `AlertDialogDescription` | `PlatformAlertDialogContent`, `PlatformAlertDialogTitle`, `PlatformAlertDialogDescription` |
| `AlertDialogCancel`                                | `PlatformAlertDialogCancel`                                                 |
| `Textarea`                                         | `PlatformTextarea`                                                          |

## Prohibited Imports

These imports are BANNED in `src/components/platform/**/*.tsx`:

```typescript
// ❌ NEVER use these in platform files
import { Card } from '@/components/ui/card';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button';
import { Input } from '@/components/ui/input';
import { Label } from '@/components/ui/label';
import { Table } from '@/components/ui/table';
import { DialogContent, DialogTitle, DialogDescription } from '@/components/ui/dialog';
import { AlertDialogContent, AlertDialogTitle, AlertDialogDescription } from '@/components/ui/alert-dialog';
import { AlertDialogCancel } from '@/components/ui/alert-dialog';
import { Textarea } from '@/components/ui/textarea';
```

## Correct Imports

```typescript
// ✅ Always use platform equivalents
import { PlatformCard, PlatformCardHeader, PlatformCardTitle, PlatformCardContent } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformCard';
import { PlatformBadge } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformBadge';
import { PlatformButton } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformButton';
import { PlatformInput } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformInput';
import { PlatformLabel } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformLabel';
import { Select, SelectValue, PlatformSelectTrigger, PlatformSelectContent, PlatformSelectItem } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformSelect';
import { PlatformTable, PlatformTableHeader, PlatformTableBody, PlatformTableHead, PlatformTableRow, PlatformTableCell } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformTable';
import { Dialog, DialogHeader, DialogFooter, PlatformDialogContent, PlatformDialogTitle, PlatformDialogDescription } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformDialog';
import { AlertDialog, AlertDialogHeader, AlertDialogFooter, AlertDialogAction, AlertDialogCancel, PlatformAlertDialogContent, PlatformAlertDialogTitle, PlatformAlertDialogDescription } from '@/components/platform/ui/PlatformDialog';
```

## Allowed Base Imports

These base imports ARE permitted (no platform equivalent needed):

- `@/components/ui/switch` — Switch
- `@/components/ui/textarea` — Textarea
- `@/components/ui/skeleton` — Skeleton
- `@/components/ui/checkbox` — Checkbox
- `@/components/ui/collapsible` — Collapsible
- `@/components/ui/avatar` — Avatar
- `@/components/ui/popover` — Popover
- `@/components/ui/dropdown-menu` — DropdownMenu
- `@/components/ui/tabs` — Tabs

## Dialog Usage

Always use `PlatformDialogContent`, `PlatformDialogTitle`, `PlatformDialogDescription` instead of base Dialog equivalents.
For AlertDialogs use `PlatformAlertDialogContent`, `PlatformAlertDialogTitle`, `PlatformAlertDialogDescription`.
Functional classNames like `max-w-2xl`, `max-h-[80vh]`, `overflow-hidden`, `flex flex-col`, `sm:max-w-md` are passed as-is — the wrapper merges them.

```tsx
// ✅ Correct — no manual dark overrides needed
<Dialog open={open} onOpenChange={onOpenChange}>
  <PlatformDialogContent className="max-w-2xl">
    <DialogHeader>
      <PlatformDialogTitle>Title</PlatformDialogTitle>
      <PlatformDialogDescription>Description</PlatformDialogDescription>
    </DialogHeader>
    ...
  </PlatformDialogContent>
</Dialog>
```

## KPI Tiles

Use `tokens.platformKpi.*` for dark-themed KPI tiles:

```tsx
import { tokens } from '@/lib/design-tokens';

<div className={tokens.platformKpi.tile}>
  <span className={tokens.platformKpi.label}>{label}</span>
  <span className={cn(tokens.platformKpi.value, colorClass)}>{value}</span>
</div>
```

## Color Palette

- Backgrounds: `bg-slate-800/50`, `bg-slate-900`
- Borders: `border-slate-700/50`, `border-slate-700`
- Text primary: `text-white`
- Text secondary: `text-slate-300`
- Text muted: `text-slate-400`
- Accent: `violet-500`, `violet-600`
- Focus: `focus:border-violet-500/50`

## Prohibited Semantic Classes

These resolve to light theme colors and must NOT be used:

- `bg-card`, `bg-background`, `bg-muted`
- `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`
- `border-border`

Use explicit slate classes instead.
